Saudi Arabia Offers 4,000 Land Plots in Hail Province, SPA Says

-- B y   W a e l   M a h d i
-- 
2011-04-03T18:15:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-03/saudi-arabia-offers-4-000-land-plots-in-hail-province-spa-says.html
Saudi Arabia  will offer 4,000 plots
of land suitable for building housing units in the northern
province of Hail, the  Saudi Press Agency  reported, citing Prince
Saud bin Abdulmohsen, the governor of Hail.  The land plots will be distributed among residents of the
province next week, SPA said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Wael Mahdi in Khobar at   wmahdi@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
